com.ak.json.nodetree

Class AbstractJNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ak.json.nodetree.AbstractJNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JInstrumentalNode, JNode, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<JNode>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JArrayNode, JObjectNode, JValueNode

    public abstract class AbstractJNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements JNode, JInstrumentalNode, java.lang.Cloneable
    Class AbstractJNode represents common methods set for different types of JNode.
    Author:
    krasnop@bellsouth.net (Alexei Krasnopolski)
